ca.athabascau.sccori.data
Class TurnInfo

java.lang.Object
  ca.athabascau.sccori.data.TurnInfo

public class TurnInfo
extends java.lang.Object

This contianer object represent the information for a single player during one of its turn. That is, the stock on hand, order received, LD1, LD2, LD3, unit cost, total cost, and the cycle number.
